### ==========================================
### 栗藏 (LiCang) API 集成测试
### 使用 VS Code REST Client 插件运行
### 基础地址: http://localhost:8080 (网关)
### ==========================================

### ========== 1. 用户注册 ==========

### 1.1 注册新用户（手机号 + 验证码 + 密码）
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "code": "123456",
  "password": "test123456"
}

### ========== 2. 用户登录 ==========

### 2.1 登录获取 Token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "password": "test123456"
}

### ========== 3. 获取用户信息 ==========

### 3.1 获取当前用户信息（使用登录返回的 token）
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/user/info
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### ========== 4. 分类管理 ==========

### 4.1 创建分类（默认分类）
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "catName": "默认分类",
  "sort": 1
}

### 4.2 创建二级分类（编程技术）
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parentId": 0,
  "catName": "编程技术",
  "sort": 2
}

### 4.3 获取分类列表（树形结构）
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### ========== 5. 收藏管理（含解析） ==========

### 5.1 创建收藏（直接传入内容）
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/collects
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Spring Boot 官方文档",
  "originUrl": "https://spring.io/projects/spring-boot",
  "resourceType": 4,
  "platform": "webpage",
  "content": "Spring Boot makes it easy to create stand-alone, production-grade Spring based Applications that you can just run. Spring Boot provides a robust framework for building microservices and web applications.",
  "summary": "Spring Boot 官方文档介绍",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "tagIds": [7]
}

### 5.2 创建收藏（携带解析请求的元信息）
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/collects
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Java 并发编程实战",
  "originUrl": "https://example.com/java-concurrency",
  "resourceType": 2,
  "platform": "zhihu",
  "content": "Java并发编程是Java开发中的核心技能之一。通过掌握线程池、锁、并发容器等机制，可以编写出高效的多线程程序。Java提供了丰富的并发工具类，如CountDownLatch、CyclicBarrier、Semaphore等。",
  "summary": "Java 并发编程核心知识点总结",
  "categoryId": 2,
  "tagIds": [7]
}

### 5.3 获取收藏列表（分页）
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/collects?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 5.4 获取收藏详情（替换 {id} 为上一步返回的 id）
# GET http://localhost:8080/v1/collects/1
# Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 5.5 更新收藏
# PUT http://localhost:8080/v1/collects/1
# Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "title": "Spring Boot 官方文档（已更新）",
#   "summary": "更新后的摘要"
# }

### 5.6 切换置顶状态
# PUT http://localhost:8080/v1/collects/1/top
# Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 5.7 更新阅读状态
# PUT http://localhost:8080/v1/collects/1/read?readStatus=1
# Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### ========== 6. 标签管理 ==========

### 6.1 获取标签列表（系统标签 + 自定义标签）
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 6.2 创建自定义标签
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tagName": "后端开发",
  "color": "#1890FF"
}

### 6.3 合并标签（将 sourceIds 合并到 targetId）
# POST http://localhost:8080/v1/tags/merge
# Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "sourceIds": [1, 2],
#   "targetId": 3
# }

### ========== 7. ES 全文搜索 ==========

### 7.1 搜索收藏（权重: title^3 > summary^2 > content）
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/collects/search?keyword=Spring&page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 7.2 搜索收藏（多关键词）
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/collects/search?keyword=Java并发&page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### ========== 8. 解析服务 ==========

### 8.1 调用解析服务解析 URL
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/parse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://spring.io/projects/spring-boot"
}

### ========== 9. 同步服务 ==========

### 9.1 创建同步记录
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "device-001",
  "syncType": 0
}

### 9.2 获取同步记录列表
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/sync?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### ========== 10. AI 服务 ==========

### 10.1 AI 分类建议
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/ai/categorize
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Spring Boot 入门教程",
  "content": "Spring Boot 是一个基于 Spring 框架的快速开发框架..."
}

### 10.2 AI 摘要生成
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/ai/summarize
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Java 并发编程",
  "content": "Java并发编程是Java开发中的核心技能之一。通过掌握线程池、锁、并发容器等机制，可以编写出高效的多线程程序。"
}

### 10.3 AI 标签推荐
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/ai/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "深入理解 JVM 虚拟机",
  "content": "JVM是Java虚拟机的缩写，是Java程序运行的基础。"
}

### ========== 11. 批量操作 ==========

### 11.1 批量标记已读
# POST http://localhost:8080/v1/collects/batch
# Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "ids": [1, 2],
#   "operateType": "MARK_READ",
#   "readStatus": 1
# }

### 11.2 批量删除
# POST http://localhost:8080/v1/collects/batch
# Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "ids": [1],
#   "operateType": "DELETE"
# }

### ========== 12. 删除收藏（单项） ==========

### 12.1 删除收藏（会同步删除 ES 索引）
# DELETE http://localhost:8080/v1/collects/1
# Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
